  "title": "DESIGNATING THE MONTH OF FEBRUARY 2026 AS \u201cCAREER AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION MONTH\u201d IN THE STATE OF DELAWARE.",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}",
